	<h1 class="title">去海边度假的话，这里有几个不太贵的海上木屋推荐</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/113313/small/113313.jpg?1434099367" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">马梦涵 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-08 19:35:13 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18670/medium/18670.png?1449508614" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


